{"tid":803294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【現代文字獄】「習豬頭最近怎麼樣」 網民被行拘10天","createTime":"2018-09-02T07:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T12:09:12.000Z","uid":22675,"like":107,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"204a12de266ab089daf04f3c5b1168d8d19ddeb5","tid":803294,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:03:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180901/58633763\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180901%2F58633763&d=nP0iKoujsGWWgNThry21MMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f8982699\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180901%2F58633763&h=ae689e40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180901/58633763</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180901/large/1535796171_7503.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180901%2Flarge%2F1535796171_7503.jpg&h=488b41f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海南三亞市天涯區水蛟村一名網民，7月19日在微信群組發言「習豬頭最近怎麼樣了，好幾年沒看新聞聯播了」，1個月後被當地公安機關傳喚接受調查，並處以行政拘留10日，罰款500元人民幣（約574港元）。<br />\n<br />\n根據三亞市公安局天涯分局行政處罰決定書顯示，被告倪華平（39歲），初中教育程度，於7月19日晚上9時33分在三亞市水蛟村對面出租屋內休息時，因自己覺得社會不公平，使用手機微信在一個名叫「邵陽被販小孩尋親團」的群組發出一句：「習豬頭最近怎麼樣了，好幾年沒看新聞聯播了」，以此來發洩內心的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n直至上月20日中午12時20分許，倪華平在出租屋內被警方傳召到公安機關接受調。經查問，倪承認公然侮辱他人，根據《中華人民共和國治安管理處罰法》第四十二條第二項規定，對倪華平處以行拘並罰款。"},{"pid":"d4215cd770c2036d601900112a622cbb8734b9be","tid":803294,"uid":2126,"like":169,"dislike":0,"score":169,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:09:08.000Z","msg":"全世界又唔係得佢姓習<br />\n見到豬頭就覺得人地話緊佢?"},{"pid":"2af4457ed155147d69be34b47610560fb46aded6","tid":803294,"uid":22675,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:11:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dl5eZ0_UcAAXKdv.jpg\" data-thu